OL,4,Csecure financial settlement from MoD
OL,6,FThe family of a man shot dead by the
OL,7,FBritish Army in 1971 have secured a
OL,8,Ffinancial settlement from the Ministry
OL,9,Fof Defence.
OL,11,FBilly McGreanery, 41, was shot at the
OL,12,Fjunction of Eastway, Lonemoor Road and
OL,13,FWestland Street in Londonderry, late
OL,14,Fin the evening of September 14, 1971.
OL,16,FHe underwent surgery at Altnagelvin
OL,17,Fhospital but died during the early
OL,18,Fhours of September 15.
