OL,6,FThe family received a public apology
OL,7,Fin 2013 from then Armed Forces
OL,8,Fminister Andrew Robathan speaking in
OL,9,Fthe House of Commons, and they
OL,10,Frequested that a fresh inquest was
OL,11,Fconducted in his death.
OL,13,FThe case was referred to Northern
OL,14,FIreland's Public Prosecution Service
OL,15,F(PPS) in 2017 who directed to the PSNI
OL,16,Fto carry out a number of inquiries.
OL,18,FFollowing an investigation, the PPS
OL,19,Ftook the decision not to prosecute an
OL,20,Findividual known as Soldier A in
OL,21,Frelation to Mr McGreanery's death.
