OL,6,FThe family have requested a review of
OL,7,Fthis decision which is ongoing.
OL,9,FEarlier this year, the Attorney
OL,10,FGeneral for Northern Ireland, Dame
OL,11,FBrenda King, directed a fresh inquest
OL,12,Finto the circumstances of Billy's
OL,13,Fdeath.
OL,15,FHowever, this did not take place
OL,16,Fbecause of the Legacy Act which halted
OL,17,Fall legacy inquests.
