OL,6,FMr McGreanery's nephew who is also
OL,7,Fcalled Billy McGreanery said they
OL,8,Fstill hope to get justice over his
OL,9,Funcle's death.
OL,11,F"In my opinion, today the Ministry of
OL,12,FDefence have made a financial
OL,13,Fretribution for the death, pain,
OL,14,Fanguish and sorrow they have inflicted
OL,15,Fon our family," he said.
