OL,6,F"I liken this process to a three-
OL,7,Fcourse meal that we fought very hard
OL,8,Ffor and earned. The starter was the
OL,9,Fapologies for the wrongful killing of
OL,10,FBilly, and today is the dessert,
OL,11,Ffinancial retribution, but they
OL,12,Fskipped the main course ` justice `
OL,13,Fwhich we have hungered for for 53
OL,14,Fyears, and for which we can only hope."
OL,16,FHe added: "The PPS review puts the
OL,17,Fjustice we crave firmly on the plate,
OL,18,Fand only a prosecution will satisfy
OL,19,Four need for the justice we rightly
OL,20,Fdeserve."
