OL,6,FSolicitor Gary Duffy, who acts for the
OL,7,FMcGreanery family, said the settlement
OL,8,Fis long overdue.
OL,10,F"Today's settlement is a long overdue,
OL,11,Fbut nevertheless, welcome endorsement
OL,12,Fof the family's campaign to uncover
OL,13,Fthe truth around this unjustified and
OL,14,Funjustifiable killing by a soldier in
OL,15,Fthe British army," he said.
