OL,6,F"This case highlights the value and
OL,7,Fmerit of such legacy civil actions in
OL,8,Ftruth recovery and obtaining justice.
OL,9,FFurthermore, it exemplifies the need
OL,10,Fto move beyond the Legacy Act and its
OL,11,Fbar to prosecutions and inquests.
OL,13,F"We look forward to the reinstatement
OL,14,Fof the family's inquest and for a
OL,15,Fdecision on the prosecution of the
OL,16,Fsoldier who shot and killed Billy."
