OL,6,F"Over a decade ago both the British
OL,7,Fgovernment and the Ministry of Defence
OL,8,Fapologised to the family of Billy
OL,9,FMcGreanery following a review by the
OL,10,FHET that found that their uncle was
OL,11,Funarmed and posed no threat when
OL,12,FSoldier A shot and killed him back in
OL,13,F1971," she said.
OL,15,F"Today's settlement is another
OL,16,Facknowledgement for the wrong done
OL,17,Fthat day and is welcomed by the
OL,18,FMcGreanery family.
