OL,6,F"William McGreanery's family has been
OL,7,Fsteadfast in their campaign for truth,
OL,8,Fjustice and accountability. For more
OL,9,Fthan 50 years, all they have sought is
OL,10,Finformation about what happened to
OL,11,FWilliam and justice for those who
OL,12,Fkilled him.
OL,14,F"Today's settlement is undoubtedly
OL,15,Fgood news for the family and
OL,16,Fvindicates their decades long
OL,17,Fcampaign. Unfortunately, however, it
OL,18,Fdoes not deliver the justice they are
OL,19,Fentitled to and have fought so long to
OL,20,Fsecure.
